      "author": "semanticdata",
      "description": "New front matter link processing feature! Now Influx will see those page links in your front matter!\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n\r\n* Add documentation deployment workflow by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/100\r\n* Fix: max line width to respect obsidian readable line length option by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/101\r\n* Feature/Refactor: extract pure functions and add frontmatter processing by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/102\r\n* Fix: memory leak in previewFileHashes and previewReactRoots by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/103\r\n* Fix: async performance improvements by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/104\r\n* Fix: dom performance issues via direct dom manipulation by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/105\r\n* Fix: refresh and update patterns and performance items by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/106\r\n* Fix: only generate stylesheets on settings change (triggerUpdates) by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/107\r\n* Chores: remove dead code and optimize by @semanticdata in https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/pull/108\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/jensmtg/influx/compare/2.2.2...2.3.0",
